 Honors program application 

 
 

  










    
 Please be sure you have reviewed  the program details and eligibility requirements  before applying.  
     Please submit your Bren School of ICS Honors Application by noon on Monday June, 1st.</strong> 
    Please inform your 2 Bren School faculty references that they must access the reference form via the Bren School faculty intranet and submit it by June 1.</strong> 
    For further information, please contact the Bren School Student Affairs office at (949) 824-5156, or send email to  ucounsel@uci.edu . 
   
    

